[2026-04-14T17:05:08.728Z] OUT <message from='local_30100032@conference.localhost/admin' to='140000228@localhost/evejs' type='groupchat' id='evejs-1776186308727-1'><body>{&quot;cmd&quot;:&quot;speak&quot;,&quot;charid&quot;:1,&quot;messageText&quot;:&quot;&lt;b&gt;&lt;color=0xfff4d35e&gt;Welcome to EveJS Elysian.&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt; A lot already works, but you &lt;color=0xffff8080&gt;will&lt;/color&gt; still find bugs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=0xff80d8ff&gt;@Icey&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt; founded this project. Without him, none of this exists.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=0xffffc266&gt;@John Elysian&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt; is the reason you can undock, warp, fire missiles, use the market, experience time dilation, and touch a long list of other core systems. A lot of this took weeks of 24/7 work to get running against the latest client, and some of it simply had not been done properly before.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; Big respect as well to &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=0xffd7bde2&gt;EvE-MU&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt; for proving this path was possible long before AI tools existed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=0xff9be564&gt;@Deer_Hunter&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt; helped keep development alive when the costs were make-or-break. Thank you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;color=0xffff8080&gt;If you hit a bug, please report it in the Discord linked on the EveJS Elysian GitHub and include exact steps to reproduce it.&lt;/color&gt;&quot;}</body></message>
[2026-04-14T17:05:31.527Z] OUT <message from='local_30100032@conference.localhost/admin' to='140000228@localhost/evejs' type='groupchat' id='evejs-1776186331526-2'><body>{&quot;cmd&quot;:&quot;speak&quot;,&quot;charid&quot;:1,&quot;messageText&quot;:&quot;Spawned 3 transient Drifter Battleship /drifter hulls on the native NPC path. Drifter hull effects, turbo-shield presentation, and superweapon sequencing now ride the native combat path instead of a fake fitted-module harness.&quot;}</body></message>
